    "body": "Electron reads the `text-scaling-factor` setting of `org.gnome.desktop.interface` to get the DPI, you can set it to a proper value to make Electron work correctly. Also you can use the [web-frame](https://github.com/atom/electron/blob/master/docs/api/web-frame.md#webframesetzoomfactorfactor) module to set page's scale factor.\n"
