    "updated_at": "2015-08-31T03:24:58Z",
    "body": "@trusktr\n\nHere's a skeleton `nvim.html`:\n\n``` html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <script>\n        var webFrame = require('web-frame');\n        webFrame.setZoomFactor(2);\n    </script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <p>Paragraph Element which should now be rescaled</p>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\nThe point is, you can use requires in the renderer (window) process.\n"
  },
